      "role": "user",
      "content": "it cut off at the end there lol. but yeah, so since there's no rain or anything for the radar to bounce off of, how do pilots actually stay safe if they can't see it coming on their instruments? is there any way to predict where those pockets might be?",
      "source": "evaluator"
